    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Portal Factory（传送门工厂）</strong> 是一款开放世界的工厂建造冒险游戏，将探索与工程完美结合！单人或与朋友一起游玩，沉浸在一个充满活力的世界中。利用先进技术的力量，建立复杂的工厂系统，实现资源采集、制作和生产的自动化。随着运营的扩大，探索世界的遥远角落，发现隐藏的地下城，解开神秘面纱并收获宝贵奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/49d1d65ec3ca602dc9fce50b8eef4bd7.poster.avif?t=1752407470\" width=654 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/49d1d65ec3ca602dc9fce50b8eef4bd7.webm?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/49d1d65ec3ca602dc9fce50b8eef4bd7.mp4?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基地建造：</strong> 设计并优化你的工厂布局，实现资源生产流程的自动化。从小型工作坊逐步扩展为庞大的工业中心。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/b87b13f2bd40ed6834c17f0f86575b8b.poster.avif?t=1752407470\" width=654 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/b87b13f2bd40ed6834c17f0f86575b8b.webm?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/b87b13f2bd40ed6834c17f0f86575b8b.mp4?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样生态：</strong> 从郁郁葱葱的森林到荒凉的沙漠，探索多种多样的地貌环境，每种都有独特的资源与挑战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/482af7af342014ef57fb227de300f52a.poster.avif?t=1752407470\" width=654 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/482af7af342014ef57fb227de300f52a.webm?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/482af7af342014ef57fb227de300f52a.mp4?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>程序生成的地下城：</strong> 深入地下城，探索未知领域。发现古老的秘密、稀有资源和强大的技术，以增强你的工厂能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/cdb37c99f0fa867d02dd7848e8b3da33.poster.avif?t=1752407470\" width=654 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/cdb37c99f0fa867d02dd7848e8b3da33.webm?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/cdb37c99f0fa867d02dd7848e8b3da33.mp4?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多人联机：</strong> 与朋友组队协作，共同打造庞大的生产网络，或一起探索这个世界。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/e92faf302bd54aabd7e2b57d7cd92776.poster.avif?t=1752407470\" width=654 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/e92faf302bd54aabd7e2b57d7cd92776.webm?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328810/extras/e92faf302bd54aabd7e2b57d7cd92776.mp4?t=1752407470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>环境危害：</strong> 在面临环境威胁的同时，高效管理你的工厂，并揭示隐藏在地表之下的危险。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好将你的工厂提升到一个新的高度了吗？建造、探索，并揭开传送门背后的神秘世界！</p>",
